name: The Marvel Super Heroes
overview: This cartoon series, characterized by extremely limited animation, features five of the most popular super-powered heroes from Marvel Comics: the Incredible Hulk, the Mighty Thor, Captain America, Iron Man, and the Sub-Mariner.

episodes.name: The Origin of Captain America
episodes.overview: Part 1 of 3. World War 2, America develops a Super Soldier formula and Steve Rogers is the first and only to take it. Becoming Captain America hiding his Identity as a army private with the help of camp mascot Bucky Barnes. Features Captain America.

episodes.name: Wreckers Among Us
episodes.overview: Part 2 of 3. Captain America's with the help of a woman known only as Agent 13,  focus on saboteurs lead by mysterious Sando (Colonel Krantz) and Omar. Features Captain America and Bucky .

episodes.name: Enter Red Skull
episodes.overview: Part 3 of 3. Captain America learns that the Red Skull is behind all the sabotage. Features Captain America and Bucky
